plates. This result has\nimportant implications for the growth of longitudinal buckling instabilities in\nsubducting spherical shells.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 11 Jul 2021 22:49:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2021 14:16:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-10"}
