resented. The total sample has a median of ${\\gamma = -2.11\n\\pm 0.03}$ (standard error), in agreement with dynamical modelling studies at\nredshift zero. The lack of evolution in total density slopes in the past 4-6\nGyrs supports a dry merging model for early-type galaxy evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 05:46:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
