naries are border line cases to\nallow an investigation of the transition between a common envelope formation\nand other mass-transfer processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 06:53:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
