 model that provides\nan experimental model system to explore further the cellular, molecular and\nphysical mechanisms involved during axonal growth, guidance and midline\ncrossing through a combination of $\\textit{in vitro}$ and $\\textit{in vivo}$\napproaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 08:06:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-13"}
