atch with the models. However, the observational sample of\nresolved binary discs is still small and additional data are required to draw\nmore robust conclusions on the flux-radius correlation and how it depends on\nthe binary properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 09:03:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
