er in our sample. No current model can\naccount for all observed properties, necessitating the development and\nrefinement of NS jet models to include magnetic field strengths up to $10^{13}$\nG. Finally, we discuss jet quenching in soft states of NS low-mass X-ray\nbinaries, the radio non-detections of all observed very-faint X-ray binaries in\nour sample, and future radio campaigns of accreting NSs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Jul 2021 09:44:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-22"}
